text: Asia Network Television (); is an Iraqi satellite television channel. It is based in Baghdad, Iraq. The channel was launched in 2012. ==Programs== * Flash Back - فلاش باك (in Arabic) * Studio Alateba - ستديو الاطباء (in Arabic) * Haraer - حراير (in Arabic) * Zahktona - زهكتونة (in Arabic) * Noqta Alsfer - نقطة الصفر (in Arabic) * Sout Almalaeb - صوت الملاعب (in Arabic) ==References== Category:2012 establishments in Asia Category:Television channels in Iraq
title: Asia Network Television
